  <scopecontent id="aspace_7d31a1ba9209e509df455986170fab4a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>A collection of clippings documenting anything related to gay people, mostly from Madison, Wisconsin newspapers for 1978-1979 and mostly from Chicago newspapers for 1980-1991. Plus photographs of gay softball teams and pride parades in Chicago in 1981 and correspondence to public officials and others about gay issues.</p>  </scopecontent>
